You are analyzing code for **AI Prompt Injection** vulnerabilities.

## What Is Prompt Injection?

Prompt injection occurs when user-supplied input is incorporated into LLM prompts without adequate separation or sanitization, allowing an attacker to override the system instructions, exfiltrate data, or cause the model to perform unintended actions. This is the AI equivalent of SQL injection — untrusted input mixed with trusted instructions in the same channel.

